#- Instructions for Gezoerskel
#- Hey Gezo,

It looks like everything left was reinforced by someone other than me. I want to get rid of everything from the second floor up. This includes interior walls and posts. Leave however everything chest wise and whatnot. Everything will be put in
#- the chest near the couch downstairs. Do NOT touch the first floor or the basement. Thanks.
#- 